  "system": {
    "description": "<p><strong>Not from the PDF's Example Starships stat blocks</strong> -- only the small-station hull row (Building a Starship, hull table) and a one-paragraph blurb exist in the source; this loadout is an original example built on that hull for this pack. A station has no Speed and no spike drive, and cannot maneuver in combat, though transit jets can slowly reposition it in-system over weeks. The Bannerjee-12 is a common civilian trade/customs station found on poor or backwater worlds with light traffic; it allows docking by bulk freighters and ships not cleared to land planetside.</p><p><strong>Cargo:</strong> 500 tons (informational estimate). <strong>Cost:</strong> 5M base price (hull table).</p>",
